OUTFIT - Designed by me 😍
MY HARDWORKER @hairgoalbysachi 

This shoot took a lot of hard work, and without my team, I couldn’t have done it. A special thanks to Sharif Bhai @time_loop_studio ❤️ & his team @muhammad_javed0001 @ahmedmirza8887 for always listening to my tantrums and crazy ideas for every shoot! 

This reel is inspired by @sumbulsultanpuri but we did it in our own unique style. Let me tell you , this was a one-month plan! I discussed this concept with a model, but unfortunately, she ditched us, took our idea to another makeup artist, and did the shoot first. I was so upset 😭 how can someone do that after planning and discussing everything for so long? She just wanted to do it quickly and get it done by someone else.😮‍💨

But never mind 🥹 our plan had to go on! And it did. Your love and support made it all worth it. Thank you so much for appreciating our hard work! ❤️✨
